# URL Shortener Configuration

## Environment Variables

Tạo file `.env` trong thư mục root:

```env
# MongoDB Configuration
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/url-shortener

# Redis Configuration (Optional)
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_ENABLED=true

# Application
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

# Base URL for shortened links (leave empty to auto-detect from request)
# Development: http://localhost:3000
# Production examples:
#   - BASE_URL=https://short.io
#   - BASE_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com
#   - BASE_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app
BASE_URL=
```

## Chạy không có Redis

Nếu chưa có Redis, bạn có thể disable Redis caching trong `src/app.module.ts`:

```typescript
// Comment out CacheModule registration
// CacheModule.registerAsync({ ... }),
```

Sau đó update `src/urls/urls.service.ts` để không inject CACHE_MANAGER:

```typescript
// Comment out cache injection
// @Inject(CACHE_MANAGER) private cacheManager: Cache,
```

App vẫn chạy bình thường, chỉ không có caching layer.
